  <name>Spreadsheet</name>
  <summary>Create simple and beautiful spreadsheets</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      A spreadsheet app that lets you create simple and beautiful spreadsheets.
    </p>
    <p>Features include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Keyboard shortcuts for better experience. You can use your accustomed keyboard shortcuts e.g. Ctrl + Z to undo, Ctrl + Shift + Z to redo, etc.</li>
      <li>Save your works automatically. Your sheets are saved automatically when created or changed.</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
